---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Client Results | MapPulse Local SEO"
  description="Real results from real Gulf Coast businesses. See how MapPulse helps Mississippi businesses rank on Google Maps and grow their customer base."
>
  <Header activePage="Results" />

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Client Results</span>
      <h1>Real businesses.<br/>Real numbers.</h1>
      <p>Every client below is a Gulf Coast small business we helped get found on Google. No stock photos, no made-up metrics — just honest work and what it produced.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section results-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="results-grid">
        <!-- Sudsy Co -->
        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="result-header">
            <span class="result-category">Home Services — Appliance Rentals</span>
            <h2>Sudsy Co. Washer & Dryer Rentals</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Website build and local SEO for a Gulf Coast appliance rental company serving Gulfport, Biloxi, Ocean Springs, Gautier, and Pascagoula. Mobile-first site with service area pages, structured data, and a Google Business Profile tuned to rank for "washer dryer rental near me" across South Mississippi.</p>
          <div class="result-metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">↑</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Organic Traffic</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">5+</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Cities Ranking</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">GBP</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Fully Optimized</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://www.sudsycorentals.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="result-link">Visit Site →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Jackson County MS -->
        <div class="result-card featured">
          <div class="result-header">
            <span class="result-category">Directory Network — Local SEO</span>
            <h2>JacksonCountyMS.com</h2>
          </div>
          <p>The flagship directory in the MapPulse network — a hyper-local business directory covering all of Jackson County, MS. Built from the ground up with city guides, coupons, and an SEO structure designed to rank for "businesses in [city]" searches countywide. The directory is the lead engine that powers MapPulse.</p>
          <div class="result-metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">800+</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Business Listings</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">6</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Cities Covered</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">Live</span>
              <span class="metric-label">& Growing</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://www.jacksoncountyms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="result-link">Visit Site →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Harrison County MS -->
        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="result-header">
            <span class="result-category">Directory Network — Local SEO</span>
            <h2>HarrisonCountyMS.com</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Expanded the directory network to Harrison County — Biloxi, Gulfport, D'Iberville, Long Beach, and Pass Christian. Same hyper-local approach with category pages, location pages, and deal listings that bring in searchers looking for local businesses.</p>
          <div class="result-metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">1,000+</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Business Listings</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">5</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Cities Covered</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">Live</span>
              <span class="metric-label">& Growing</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://www.harrisoncountyms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="result-link">Visit Site →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Hancock County MS -->
        <div class="result-card">
          <div class="result-header">
            <span class="result-category">Directory Network — Local SEO</span>
            <h2>HancockCountyMS.com</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Completed the tri-county coverage with Hancock County — Bay St. Louis, Waveland, Diamondhead, and surrounding areas. The full directory network now covers the entire Mississippi Gulf Coast.</p>
          <div class="result-metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">400+</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Business Listings</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">4</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Cities Covered</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">Live</span>
              <span class="metric-label">& Growing</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://www.hancockcountyms.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="result-link">Visit Site →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <h2>Want results like these?</h2>
        <p>We start every engagement with a free local SEO audit — no cost, no obligation, just a straight answer about where your business stands online.</p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Get Your Free Audit →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: var(--blue-50);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--blue-600);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .results-section {
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .results-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .result-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--blue-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .result-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--teal-500);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-50) 0%, rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.05) 100%);
  }

  .result-header {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .result-category {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--teal-600);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .result-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .result-card > p {
    color: var(--blue-600);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .result-metrics {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .metric {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .metric-value {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--teal-600);
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--blue-600);
  }

  .result-link {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--teal-600);
  }

  .result-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: var(--blue-50);
  }

  .cta-box {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal-600) 0%, var(--teal-500) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .cta-box h2 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .cta-box .btn {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--teal-600);
  }

  .cta-box .btn:hover {
    background: var(--blue-900);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .results-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .result-card.featured {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
  }
</style>
